title: Mathis Bridge scheduled to close Oct. 30
text:
Published By: Asbury Park Press - Today 
Drivers beware: the eastbound Thomas A. Mathis Bridge over Barnegat Bay is slated to close for repairs at 9 p.m. Oct. 30. ...
